   <text>
      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Sculture MASTROIANNI Roma </s>
               <s> Edizione Propria N. 13 </s>
               <s> "Cromogliptica" A. Marzi - Roma  </s>
               <s> A te fiore tra i fiori </s>
               <s> A toi fleur parmi les fleure </s>
               <s> Riproduzione interdetta </s>
               <s> Stampata in Italia </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>A te fiore tra i fiori</head>
               <figDesc>In primo piano una donna vestita di bianco con in mano un mazzo di fiori. 
                        Sulla sinistra un uomo in ginocchio verso la donna. 
                  </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            li 9/12-1916</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p>
                     <lb/>            Oliva,<lb/>            Sono felice di annunziarti che <lb/>            salvo complicazioni per il giorno <lb/>            di Natale sarò a casa ed il primo <lb/>            del novello anno sarò da te.<lb/>            Io spero che questi pochi giorni <lb/>            che mi restano d'ansia <lb/>            posfa pasfarli quietamente. <lb/>            Anche da Spezia seguiterò a scri-<lb/>            verti giornalmente e ti darò <lb/>            più volte indicazioni. <lb/>            Per tanto il fuoco ardente che <lb/>            m'arde nelle vene <gap reason="illegible"/>
                     <lb/>
                     <gap reason="illegible"/> vigore pensando che presto <lb/>            potrò riabbracciarti. Ora ho molto <lb/>            da fare per le consegne. <lb/>            Amami tanto  </p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <s>
                     <lb/>un bacio tuo <signed>
                        <persName>
                           <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                        </persName>
                     </signed>
                  </s>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 22 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
